http://www.undp.org/content/dam/undp/documents/projects/AZE/Final Project Report  Solid Waste Management Azerbaijan Jan 29.docx

outputs.output_descr: The project aims making necessary improvements in laws, Regulations, norms and standards, in determining per capita waste generation capacity in the country, creation of the National Solid Waste Data Bank, conducting feasibility studies and preparing planning guidelines, and conducting a small-scale solid waste management improvement pilot project in one of the rural areas of the country.

project_descr: Solid Waste Management Improvement in Azerbaijan by exploring multi-sector partnerships approaches.
